<table role="presentation" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td class="content">
      <h2>Work Order Submitted for Your Request</h2>
      <p>
        The vendor assigned to your maintenance request <strong><%= request.mruid %></strong> has submitted a work order. The property manager is currently reviewing it — no action is required from you at this time.
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td class="content" style="padding-top: 0;">
      <div class="detail-card">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Summary</h3>
        <table class="detail-table">
          <tr>
            <td class="detail-label">Request #</td>
            <td class="detail-value"><%= request.mruid %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="detail-label">Title</td>
            <td class="detail-value"><%= request.title %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="detail-label">Estimated Cost</td>
            <td class="detail-value">$<%= (workOrder.estimatedCostInCents / 100).toFixed(2) %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="detail-label">Scope</td>
            <td class="detail-value"><%= workOrder.scope %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
    </td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td class="content">
      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">
        You'll receive another update once the work order is reviewed and the vendor is ready to begin.
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
